{"tid":2389733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府根本係度誤導市民 (有圖)","createTime":"2021-02-01T05:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T06:04:00.000Z","uid":391116,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f947f26467d3c20e455360583c71a93442a40f32","tid":2389733,"uid":391116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"每一日淨係報導每一日有幾多個人確診<br />\n但係就無講過其實由頭到尾有幾多人好返<br />\n真心有幾多個市民真係會上網咁樣睇？<br />\n每日聽新聞都有咁多人確診<br />\n搞到個個都心驚膽跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你仲唔係誤導市民？<br />\n然後攬炒成個市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFPn6RR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFPn6RR.png&h=d0e46bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家睇返張圖<br />\n出院/痊愈率 已經高達89%<br />\n而死亡+危殆 只有2%<br />\n仲接受治療 係9%<br />\n<br />\n利申: 我只係想夜晚可以出街食下飯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我食撚夠外賣啦，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720337778b4c1a944f3601e25c6b07cbbff44bb0","tid":2389733,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}